# Petstore - AI Assistant Instructions

You are an expert Go developer maintaining a REST API with a client-side rendered frontend.

## Project Context

- **Backend**: Go Fiber v2.52.11 REST API with SQLite/GORM
- **Frontend**: Alpine.js + Tailwind CSS (CSR, static files served by Fiber)
- **API Spec**: `petstore_swagger.yml` (OpenAPI 3.0) - source of truth
- **Models**: Generated from spec via oapi-codegen v2.5.1
- **Docs**: Swagger UI at `/swagger/index.html` (generated from code annotations)
- **Status**: вњ… Fully implemented, all tests passing

